<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷把六个大红薯放进一个袋子里，然后递给亨德森叔叔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“2.5美元！” 凯蒂说，“谢谢您！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请给我三个南瓜。” 戴格斯特叔叔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天是柳树溪丰收节，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38823</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>多诺万一家人都在帮爷爷卖园子里的农作物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47436</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>胡萝卜、洋葱、红薯 、苹果，黄瓜和萝卜摆满了爷爷的桌子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47437</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>地上放着大大的南瓜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56009</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“能帮我把这个南瓜拿到车上去吗？” 拼客太太说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56010</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60366</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要三个苹果。” 邮递员杰夫说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60367</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的萝卜多少钱？” 可芙老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“乔伊在哪儿？” 妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们需要帮助！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73631</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“刚才我还看见她在那儿呢！” 亨德森叔叔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73632</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77104</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她在听乡村乐队唱歌。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77105</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“凯蒂，你快去把她叫回来！” 妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85005</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂跑着穿过小镇公园里的人群。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85006</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看见乔伊在跟着乡村音乐摇晃身体。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89823</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“乔伊！” 凯蒂喊道，“妈妈叫你回去帮忙！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊没注意到凯蒂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当乐队演奏结束时，乔伊和人群一起鼓掌欢呼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103430</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108279</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，一个穿着牛仔背带裤的女孩儿走上了舞台。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110695</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拿着一把小提琴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110696</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117963</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“让我们欢迎这个来自柯比维尔的小提琴手——玛吉·道威尔！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117964</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 主持人喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看！她跟我们一样大。” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130044</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂看见玛吉拿起她的小提琴开始演奏民谣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130045</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>刚开始，她演奏的音乐缓慢而悠扬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134421</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138357</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“告诉妈妈我马上就回去。” 乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138358</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140206</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想再听一曲。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140207</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧！” 凯蒂说。可是，她也没动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛吉的小提琴演奏越来越生动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她跟着节奏跺着右脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156780</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的琴弓划过琴弦， 在空中扬起了灰尘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156781</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真希望我也能像她那样拉小提琴！” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169294</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快，乔伊。” 凯蒂提醒她，“我们得去帮爷爷。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169295</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天下午晚些时候，多诺万一家人坐在野餐桌前吃炸鱼和玉米棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“沙莉姨妈和卢克来了！” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188300</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拉里的爸爸刚才在 ‘巨大南瓜大赛’ 上得了第一名！” 卢克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188301</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191740</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他的南瓜有100多磅重！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191741</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们卖光了所有的南瓜。” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200558</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们的目标完成了吗？” 沙莉姨妈问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200559</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，完成了。” 爷爷说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们挣的钱够买明年的种子了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210957</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还可以修理园子栅栏。” 爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210958</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊对南瓜和种子不感兴趣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她只想聊一件事情——玛吉的小提琴演奏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们应该听听那个女孩儿的演奏！” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224393</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的！她很棒！” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她跳起来，开心地演奏着想象中的小提琴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她又一下子坐下，拿起玉米棒吃了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242412</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过，有谁会想每天都一直练习呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242413</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不介意练习。” 乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“能像玛吉那样演奏的话，我愿意做任何事情。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们曾祖母在比你们还小的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254488</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258196</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>得到了她的第一把小提琴。” 爷爷说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258197</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她的爸爸甚至到贝兹市给她买了一把一半大小的小提琴，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那是德国制造的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你们俩见过曾祖母就好了。” 爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我真想听听她的演奏。” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那把小提琴在哪儿呢？” 爷爷说，“在阁楼？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可能在上面。” 妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288539</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊很感兴趣。“您还留着它呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288540</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，是的。” 爷爷说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295562</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她是绝对不会卖了她的第一把小提琴的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以找找吗？” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咱们明天早上找找看。” 爷爷说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许你们中的一个人会想试试。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂擦了擦下巴上的黄油。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309980</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312823</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不感兴趣。” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我感兴趣！” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>